    "This is an open access article under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License",
    "Vilnius, Lithuania This question will explore the key contrasts in the vowel and consonant inventories, syllable structures, and intonation patterns of both languages.",
    "Understanding these differences will provide the foundation for analyzing how they affect language learners.",
    "How do these differences affect language learners' pronunciation and listening skills?",
    "By investigating common pronunciation errors and listening difficulties, this question will focus on how phonetic differences hinder Azerbaijani speakers learning English and English speakers learning Azerbaijani."
  ]
}